description: The total number of cases now stands at 139, with six receiving treatment at Noble's Hospital.
title: Coronavirus Isle of Man: 12 more cases confirmed
title_page: Coronavirus Isle of Man: 12 more cases confirmed - BBC News
maintext: A range of measures have been introduced to combat the spread of the virus and ease the pressure on the Manx NHS, including the closure of all but essential shops and the introduction of a temporary 40mph national speed limit.
